---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Refund Policy - OptyP">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-20 px-6">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Refund Policy</h1>
    <p class="mb-6">
      We strive to deliver high-quality resume and profile optimization services. If you are not satisfied with our service, please review the refund terms below.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">Refund Eligibility</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-6">
      <li>Refund requests must be made within 7 days of the service delivery date.</li>
      <li>Refunds are considered only if the service was not delivered as agreed or with significant quality issues.</li>
      <li>Services that have been completed or approved by the customer are not eligible for refunds.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">Refund Process</h2>
    <p>
      To request a refund, contact <a href="mailto:contact@optyp.com" class="text-primary-600 underline">contact@optyp.com</a> with your order details and reason for refund. Our support team will review your request within 5 business days.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
      For questions regarding refunds, reach out at <a href="mailto:info@optyp.com" class="text-primary-600 underline">contact@optyp.com</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
